'''GlobalSight '''是一个在[[Apache许可证|Apache许可证2.0]]下发布的开源[[翻译|翻译]]管理系统（TMS）。<ref name="globalsight.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalsight.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&catid=28%3Acategory-for-news&id=78%3Aintroducing-globalsight-71&Itemid=69 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2021-02-06 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714132700/http://www.globalsight.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&catid=28%3Acategory-for-news&id=78%3Aintroducing-globalsight-71&Itemid=69 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 从7.1版开始，它支持TMX和SRX 2.0 [[本地化行业标准协会|本地化行业标准协会]]标准。<ref name="lisa.org">{{cite web| title=The GlobalSight Open Source Initiative – Get Involved!| author=Gary Prioste| url=http://www.lisa.org/globalizationinsider/2008/11/the_globalsight.html| publisher=Lisa.org| date=2008-11| accessdate=2010-09-26| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110102144022/http://www.lisa.org/globalizationinsider/2008/11/the_globalsight.html| archivedate=2011-01-02}}</ref> 它用[[Java|Java编程语言]]开发，使用[[MySQL|MySQL]]数据库。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.translationdirectory.com/articles/article1829.php| title=Interview with Gary Prioste VP of Technology Solutions, Welocalize| publisher=ClientSide News Magazine| date=2008-11| accessdate=2010-09-26| archive-date=2021-01-26| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126022612/https://www.translationdirectory.com/articles/article1829.php| dead-url=no}}</ref> GlobalSight还支持[[计算机辅助翻译|计算机辅助翻译]]和[[机器翻译|机器翻译]]。

==历史==

从1997年到2005年，它被称为Ambassador Suite，是由GlobalSight公司开发和拥有。根据[[红鲱鱼杂志|红鲱鱼杂志]]，GlobalSight公司是1999年“十家最值得期待的公司”之一。 <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.infomanagementcenter.com/enewsletter/2009/200902/fourth.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-09-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713031344/http://www.infomanagementcenter.com/enewsletter/2009/200902/fourth.htm |archivedate=2011-07-13 }}</ref> 在2005年Transware公司收购了GlobalSight，并继续它的开发。 2008年5月[[Welocalize|Welocalize]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.welocalize.com/ |title=Welocalize |accessdate=2010-09-26 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125224223/https://www.welocalize.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 收购了Transware，同时也得到了GlobalSight。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalsight.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=2&Itemid=73 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2021-02-06 |archive-date=2009-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090129170409/http://globalsight.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=2&Itemid=73 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在用开源组件更换了产品中使用的专有技术（工作流，数据库，对象关系映射，中间件，目录管理和调度）之后，<ref name="lisa.org"/> Welocalize于2009年1月发布了开源的7.1版。<ref name="globalsight.com"/>

